summary: In honor of the loving dog pasting away 8-11-2001 to 7-11- 2012, Mischu, I always remember you.
descriptionHtml: After my dog mischu passing, she was a great dog you can say she was a gamer dog, she always like watching me play, always sitting on my lap and following what happening in the game,so after long hours reviewing and learning from tutorials, this is my first mod and im happen to have her as a follower in skyrim, but im not done i need help on creating a custom skin of her color.
author: ZeusFuryOmega
